<br>
This is wyldbuffalo, Leader of Lords of Ale and the &quot;twink worthless monk&quot; he was so adament about yelling at.  I dont hold warders responsible and i made sure nobody else has...i have stated it before, you have a descent guild, but i also stated that what roren did no justice to you guys...now i know and i have talked it over, your guild is always welcome to our events...but LoA standards, roren made our black list...it takes a LOT of work to get off of that list...rest of Warders is welcome to our events.<br>
<br>
As for punishing him...i agree, this has been drug out pretty long, you are correct roren...but Gwaeron only flames when he has reason, and he had about drop'd it...but apparently you emailed his HOME email and tried to verbally attack him again, hence his huge Flame post.  <br>
<br>
Aerch, i understand the problems as i have just recently taken over the Guild Leader Tag, but i've been in the game too long and know how it goes even when wasnt a leader.  Removing his officer tag would be good, to at least limit the damage done and lower even more if some situation as such occurs again.<br>
<br>
I am sorry to see that such a person would act that way for a guild w/good standings...and i am stating this..LoA has no probs w/Warders...but roren is ban'd from any of our events...rest of your guild is more than welcome to join us thru proper signing up or thru pick up raids.  Hopefully Roren's one big screw up w/a LOT of guilds wont hender LoA and WoN from future fighting.<br>
